author: Justin Bergman, Associated Press
title: Djokovic defeats Murray to reach Shanghai Masters final
text: Photo: Andy Wong, AP Novak Djokovic of Serbia celebrates after winning his semifinal match against Andy Murray of Britain in the Shanghai Masters tennis tournament in Shanghai, China, Saturday, Oct. 17, 2015. Novak Djokovic of Serbia celebrates after winning his semifinal... SHANGHAI (AP) — Novak Djokovic has made winning so routine this year that even when he dominates one of his biggest rivals, he takes it in stride.
